data.description:
This exquisite townhome offers an unparalleled combination of convenience, comfort, and community. Nestled in a prime location this is the ideal place to call home. Step inside and you'll immediately be impressed by the spacious and inviting layout. The open-concept living area creates a warm and welcoming atmosphere, perfect for both relaxing and entertaining guests. The heart of the home is the fully equipped kitchen, complete with sleek countertops and ample cabinet space. Upstairs, you'll find the generously sized bedrooms for every family member or guest. The master bedroom boasts his and hers walk in closest! Highlighting the private patio, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or host a BBQ. Additionally you have a detached Garage and 1 reserved parking space. The community park is close by for play time, outdoor recreation, picnics, or casual strolls.

With its unbeatable location minutes away from DIA, shopping, light rail station, restaurants, breweries, Costco, and the Gaylord Resort this townhome offers a lifestyle that is hard to beat.
